    "content": "# Modern CSS Techniques: Grid, Flexbox, and Beyond\n\nModern CSS provides powerful tools for creating responsive, maintainable layouts. Let's explore the most important techniques.\n\n## CSS Grid: Two-Dimensional Layouts\n\nCSS Grid excels at creating complex, two-dimensional layouts:\n\n```css\n.grid-container {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n  grid-gap: 2rem;\n  padding: 2rem;\n}\n\n.grid-item {\n  background: #f5f5f5;\n  padding: 1rem;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n}\n\n/* Named grid lines */\n.layout {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: \n    [sidebar-start] 250px \n    [sidebar-end main-start] 1fr \n    [main-end];\n  grid-template-rows:\n    [header-start] 60px\n    [header-end content-start] 1fr\n    [content-end footer-start] 40px\n    [footer-end];\n}\n```\n\n## Flexbox: One-Dimensional Layouts\n\nFlexbox is perfect for one-dimensional layouts and component alignment:\n\n```css\n.flex-container {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: row;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.flex-item {\n  flex: 1; /* Grow and shrink equally */\n}\n\n.flex-item:first-child {\n  flex: 0 0 200px; /* Don't grow/shrink, fixed 200px */\n}\n\n/* Centering technique */\n.center {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  align-items: center;\n  min-height: 100vh;\n}\n```\n\n## CSS Custom Properties (Variables)\n\nCreate maintainable, dynamic styles:\n\n```css\n:root {\n  --primary-color: #3b82f6;\n  --secondary-color: #64748b;\n  --spacing-unit: 1rem;\n  --border-radius: 8px;\n  --transition: 0.2s ease-in-out;\n}\n\n.button {\n  background: var(--primary-color);\n  color: white;\n  padding: calc(var(--spacing-unit) * 0.5) var(--spacing-unit);\n  border-radius: var(--border-radius);\n  transition: all var(--transition);\n}\n\n.button:hover {\n  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary-color) 80%, black);\n}\n\n/* Dark mode with custom properties */\n[data-theme=\"dark\"] {\n  --primary-color: #60a5fa;\n  --background: #0f172a;\n  --text: #f1f5f9;\n}\n```\n\n## Container Queries\n\nResponsive design based on container size:\n\n```css\n.card-container {\n  container-type: inline-size;\n  container-name: card;\n}\n\n.card {\n  padding: 1rem;\n}\n\n@container card (min-width: 400px) {\n  .card {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;\n    gap: 2rem;\n    padding: 2rem;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Modern Selectors\n\nUse advanced selectors for cleaner markup:\n\n```css\n/* :has() - parent selector */\n.card:has(.urgent) {\n  border-left: 4px solid red;\n}\n\n/* :where() - specificity control */\n:where(h1, h2, h3) {\n  margin-top: 0;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n}\n\n/* :is() - selector grouping */\n:is(article, section) :is(h1, h2) {\n  color: var(--heading-color);\n}\n\n/* nth-child with expressions */\n.grid-item:nth-child(4n + 1) {\n  grid-column: span 2;\n}\n```\n\n## CSS Logical Properties\n\nFuture-proof layouts for international applications:\n\n```css\n.element {\n  /* Instead of margin-left/right */\n  margin-inline: 1rem;\n  \n  /* Instead of margin-top/bottom */\n  margin-block: 2rem;\n  \n  /* Instead of border-left */\n  border-inline-start: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n  \n  /* Instead of text-align: left */\n  text-align: start;\n}\n```\n\n## Modern Units\n\nUse modern CSS units for better responsive design:\n\n```css\n.container {\n  /* Viewport units */\n  min-height: 100vh;\n  width: 100vw;\n  \n  /* Container query units */\n  padding: 2cqi; /* 2% of container inline size */\n  \n  /* Dynamic viewport units (mobile-friendly) */\n  height: 100dvh; /* Dynamic viewport height */\n}\n\n.typography {\n  /* Fluid typography */\n  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 3rem);\n  \n  /* Relative units */\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  margin-bottom: 1.5em;\n}\n```\n\n## Performance Optimizations\n\nOptimize CSS for better performance:\n\n```css\n/* Use transform and opacity for animations */\n.fade-in {\n  opacity: 0;\n  transform: translateY(20px);\n  transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.fade-in.visible {\n  opacity: 1;\n  transform: translateY(0);\n}\n\n/* Contain layout shifts */\n.image-container {\n  aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.image-container img {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  object-fit: cover;\n}\n\n/* Use will-change sparingly */\n.animated-element {\n  will-change: transform;\n}\n\n.animated-element.animation-complete {\n  will-change: auto;\n}\n```\n\n## Conclusion\n\nModern CSS provides powerful tools for creating responsive, maintainable layouts. By mastering Grid, Flexbox, custom properties, and modern features, you can build better user interfaces with cleaner, more efficient code.",
